3-K for All result letters were sent on July 27. If you have not received your result letter yet, please call 718-935-2009.

Please check back for updates ‐ new programs may be added in Districts 7 (South Bronx) and 23 (Brownsville, East New York, and Ocean Hill) throughout the summer!

A new 3-K for All program has been added in District 7 for the upcoming school year! To see this program, search for Concourse Village. To apply to this program, call 718-935-2009 by the August 4 deadline!
